      "<div class=\"ultp-block-item ultp-block-media post-id-176476\"><div class=\"ultp-block-content-wrap\"><div class=\"ultp-block-image ultp-block-image-opacity\"><a href=\"https://minnesotastatewire.com/one-person-dies-in-snowmobile-accident-on-arrowhead-trail-north-of-orr/\"><img alt=\"Gordon Ramsay, St. Louis County Sheriff\" fifu-featured=\"1\" post-id=\"176476\" src=\"https://d33ioocfz0fzi4.cloudfront.net/jns-media/7b/d9/27616326/webp_cjzg4ck6a4k0akm4i49ecwoilj87.webp\" title=\"Gordon Ramsay, St. Louis County Sheriff\"/></a></div><div class=\"ultp-block-content\"><h3 class=\"ultp-block-title\"><a href=\"https://minnesotastatewire.com/one-person-dies-in-snowmobile-accident-on-arrowhead-trail-north-of-orr/\">One person dies in snowmobile accident on Arrowhead Trail north of Orr</a></h3><div class=\"ultp-block-excerpt\"><p>A North Branch man died in a snowmobile accident north of Orr, Minnesota, after failing to navigate a turn and colliding with a tree. Authorities are withholding his name pending family notification while the investigation continues.</p>\n</div><div class=\"ultp-dynamic-content-group-common ultp-dynamic-content-group-1739922421473\"><div class=\"ultp-dynamic-content-field-common ultp-dynamic-content-field-1739922421473\"><p class=\"ultp-dynamic-content-field-dc\"></p></div></div><div class=\"ultp-dynamic-content-group-common ultp-dynamic-content-group-1745405235933\"><div class=\"ultp-dynamic-content-field-common ultp-dynamic-content-field-1745405235933\"><p class=\"ultp-dynamic-content-field-dc\"></p></div></div></div></div></div>"
